{"tid":2114623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒：日本政府斥資50億港元 助日企把生產線撤出中國 向世界工廠說再見","createTime":"2020-07-19T03:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T03:51:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d19a0a470f57998ae5f78a836a9cbadf13ebaf7f","tid":2114623,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"日媒指日本政府補貼口罩和酒精消毒液企業由中國遷回日本<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，日本政府將斥資700億日元，折合約50億港元，補貼在中國設廠的口罩和酒精消毒液企業，鼓勵廠商遷回日本國內或東南亞，以分散防疫相關產品的生產點及強化供應鏈。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，疫情突顯生產點集中在特定國家的風險，日本政府決定補助廠商將工廠遷出中國。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2347867&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=ad16d57b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347867</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n<br />\n真係有日本廠攞政府資助撤離中國㗎？<br />\n之前日本首相話用二千億日元資助日本企業搬離中國（&quot;China Exit&quot; Project），初頭以為無乜日本公司會捨得同世界工廠講拜拜，點知真係有㗎，仲有87間攞咗七百億起程添。<br />\n包括Hoya光學、住友橡膠、信越化工、Iris、Sharp、Shionogi（製藥）、Terumo（醫療設備）...好大嘅膽！<br />\n#係咪Brexit個朋友Chexit<br />\n報導：<br />\n<br />\n《Nikkei Asian Review》<br />\nJapan reveals 87 projects eligible for 'China exit' subsidies<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Economy/Japan-reveals-87-projects-eligible-for-China-exit-subsidies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FEconomy%2FJapan-reveals-87-projects-eligible-for-China-exit-subsidies&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=952e5423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Economy/Japan-reveals-87-projects-eligible-for-China-exit-subsidies</a>"},{"pid":"78e648622164a604c9108d7f7b82a8d7e9050eb5","tid":2114623,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1da05873625fd0f23d96585b48db9c2c108a635f","tid":2114623,"uid":127929,